data.description: Secluded mini farm located in the heart of horse country. Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is full of country charm. Multiple upgrades include a pantry, laundry room, new flooring and kitchen cabinets. Cozy master suite with new dressing room. New large front porch with amazing view of the front pasture and mountains. An excellent location to sit, relax and watch your horses and wildlife of the area. Full basement. Extremely well maintained property. Extras include a new 5 stall 52X70 horse barn, a 20X20 walk in, and large kennel. Pasture is fenced for horses. Multiple trails for horseback riding on the property. Just minutes from Grayson Highlands State Park and the Appalachian Trail. A great restaurant is just down the road. Located near Jefferson, NC. Don't let the opportunity to own this beautiful mini farm slip through your fingers.  Call me today to schedule an appointment.
